   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.320", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Pflegest\u00e4rkungsgesetze waren wichtig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.840", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch mit der Krankenhausstrukturreform haben wir wichtige Weichenstellungen vorgenommen. "
