   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.640", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Ihren Antr\u00e4gen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.920", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen der Gr\u00fcnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.920", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nennen Sie wichtige Punkte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.120", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.040", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie selbst einr\u00e4umen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.200", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schon weitgehend politisch konsentiert sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.520", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dennoch muss klar sein: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.200", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein solches Sofortprogramm reicht nicht aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.320", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen grundlegende strukturelle Ver\u00e4nderungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.280", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen einen Plan, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.720", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie die notwendigen Einzelma\u00dfnahmen zu einem Gesamtkonzept zusammengef\u00fchrt werden und wer als B\u00fcndnispartner daf\u00fcr gewonnen werden muss."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.360", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer dem Fachkr\u00e4ftemangel wirksam begegnen will, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.680", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der muss gleichzeitig die Arbeitsbedingungen verbessern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.720", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das erscheint wie die Quadratur des Kreises. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.400", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Doch nur wenn beides gleicherma\u00dfen ernst genommen wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.080", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
